{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Elementy liniowe","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":" Podsumowanie ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Elementy liniowe są elementami, które mogą wystąpić tylko w <a href=\"pl/HTML/Elementy/body\">body</a>. Od elementów blokowych odróżnia je:\n</p>\n<dl><dt id=\"zawartość_elementu\">Zawartość elementu</dt><dd> Elementy liniowe mogą zawierać tylko tekst lub inne elementy liniowe.\n</dd><dt id=\"formatowanie\">Formatowanie</dt><dd> Elementy liniowe nie tworzą nowego wiersza.\n</dd></dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elementy","title":" Elementy ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Poniżej znajduje się lista elementów \"liniowych\":\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/b\">b</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/big\">big</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/i\">i</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/small\">small</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/tt\">tt</a>\n</li><li> <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/abbr\">abbr</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/acronym\">acronym</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/cite\">cite</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/code\">code</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/dfn\">dfn</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/em\">em</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/kbd\">kbd</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/strong\">strong</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/samp\">samp</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/var\">var</a>\n</li><li> <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/a\">a</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/bdo\">bdo</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/br\">br</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/img\">img</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/map\">map</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/object\">object</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/q\">q</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/script\">script</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/span\">span</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/sub\">sub</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/sup\">sup</a>\n</li><li> <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/button\">button</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/input\">input</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/label\">label</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/select\">select</a>, <a href=\"pl/HTML/Element/textarea\">textarea</a>\n</li></ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":" Zobacz także ","isH3":true,"content":"<ul><li> <a href=\"pl/HTML/Elementy_blokowe\">Elementy blokowe</a>\n</li></ul>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n</div>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Elementy liniowe są elementami, które mogą wystąpić tylko w body. Od elementów blokowych odróżnia je:","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Inline-Elemente","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Inline elements","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Elementos en línea","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Éléments en ligne","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"インライン要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"인라인 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Elementos inline","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Строчные элементы","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"行内元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/html/inline_elements","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/html/inline_elements/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements","title":"Elementy liniowe"}],"pageTitle":"Elementy liniowe - HTML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}